  Release Info:                                                              ÃƒÆ’Ã…Â¸
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 
  Developed by Rocksteady Studios, Batman: Arkham City builds upon the
  intense, atmospheric foundation of Batman: Arkham Asylum, sending players
  soaring into Arkham City, the new maximum security "home" for all of Gotham
  City's thugs, gangsters and insane criminal masterminds. Set inside the
  heavily fortified walls of a sprawling district in the heart of Gotham
  City, this highly anticipated sequel introduces a brand-new story that
  draws together a new all-star cast of classic characters and murderous
  villains from the Batman universe, as well as a vast range of new and
  enhanced gameplay features to deliver the ultimate experience as the Dark
  Knight.
